{"tid":1390091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"示 威 者 強 烈 譴 責 天 文 台 行 為","createTime":"2019-07-31T05:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T11:43:00.000Z","uid":124630,"like":885,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"eb6fe1a348487ba074a8e0b0769087ec3a68a12b","tid":1390091,"uid":124630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:12:10.000Z","msg":"示威者強烈譴責天文台行為<br />\n＊＊＊＊<br />\n<br />\n就香港天文台報道，指熱帶氣旋韋帕於七月三十一日影響香港，並預料將會在下午兩時或以前發出八號烈風或暴風信號。示威者作出以下回應：<br />\n<br />\n發出八號烈風或暴風信號將令僱員被迫離開工作崗位，影響香港經濟。香港人素來以協助僱主工作而自豪，天文台此舉將嚴重影響市民，為市民帶來不便。<br />\n<br />\n此外，亦有指天文台此舉為配合香港示威者的不合作運動，示威者在此澄清與天文台並沒任何合作，並希望昨天受不合作運動影響而指責示威者的人士繼續上班，以免影響生計。<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n2019年7月31日（星期三）<br />\n香港時間13時10分"},{"pid":"b837063efac341107c4bea9852adab8109fdd036","tid":1390091,"uid":124630,"like":343,"dislike":1,"score":342,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WD5nYFT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWD5nYFT.png&h=a01cf0bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eff74aa041bb908fdbbcd94002bff1c1f9cd979a","tid":1390091,"uid":8213,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1dd2d31b24dc4fe28685605a943c58116380dfa","tid":1390091,"uid":124630,"like":91,"dislike":0,"score":91,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:15:51.000Z","msg":"8月5罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jxriw1u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJxriw1u.png&h=71dd5c17&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95eace21531a47316a90e7db72ec85436534af0d","tid":1390091,"uid":239384,"like":44,